    <div class="details l-contain">
         <h1 id="evening-before" class="anchored-header">
            Plan for the weekend
        </h1>
        <p>
            The whole idea behind this wedding is plain and simple: we love each other and we want to celebrate this with you. Thus, we haven’t arranged anything more than few occasions to have a good time together.
        </p>
        <h2 id="evening-before" class="anchored-header">
            Day Before (Friday the 26th of August): Warm-up
        </h2>
        <div class="details-group l-grid">
            <div class="l-grid-u">
                <p class="details-content">
                    Hopefully, most of you will be around the afternoon before the big day. We suggest we all meet for a late merenda / happy-hour / early dinner around 18h00. The informal gathering will take place at Borghesani’s:
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="l-grid-u">
                <address class="details-content">
                    <b>Casa Famiglia Borghesani</b><br>
                    <a href="https://www.google.fr/maps/@44.6108302,11.1484551,3a,75y,209.09h,73.18t/data=!3m6!1e1!3m4!1s2dPgFm-Nn1DZN40G2tBUdw!2e0!7i13312!8i6656">
                        3 via di Mezzo S. Giovanni in Persiceto <br>
                        (44.610477, 11.147852)
                    </a>
                </address>
            </div>
        </div>
        <p>
            Wooden-oven home made pizzas will be the occasion to mix and mingle! We will need you to confirm your participation  and to bring your drink(s) of choice. 
        </p>
        <h2 id="ceremony" class="anchored-header">
            The Day: Ceremony &amp; Reception
        </h2>
        <div class="details-group l-grid">
            <div class="l-grid-u">
                <p class="details-content">
                    We shall meet as early as 11.30 in the main square of Persiceto (punctuality will be crucial). The ceremony will take place at 12h00 in the City Hall. Dress code: formal. 
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="l-grid-u">
                <address class="details-content">
                    <a href="https://www.google.fr/maps/@44.6384748,11.1871749,3a,75y,289.67h,80.75t/data=!3m6!1e1!3m4!1sxmT3jFJyiX6NDxIDodn0Rw!2e0!7i13312!8i6656!6m1!1e1">
                        72 Corso Italia, S. Giovanni in Persiceto<br>
                        (44.638456, 11.186954)<br>
                    </a>
                </address>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="details-group l-grid">
            <div class="l-grid-u">
                <p class="details-content">
                    The reception will take place from 14h00 to 22h00. The Villa we choose offers a nice garden with a beautiful pool: we suggest you to bring a swimsuit and/or the necessary to change into a comfortable informal summer outif.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="l-grid-u">
                <address class="details-content">
                    <b>Villa Cortese</b><br>
                    <a href="https://www.google.fr/maps/place/Villa+Cortese/@44.6923266,10.8578406,15z/data=!4m7!1m4!3m3!1s0x477ff1dd743aba57:0xe22822b226539074!2sVia+Ponte+Alto,+35,+41011+Campogalliano+MO,+Italy!3b1!3m1!1s0x477ff1eabec356a9:0x7cb6b9070b5851f4">
                        35 via Ponte Alto, Campogalliano<br>
                        (44.692100, 10.859599)<br>
                    </a>
                </address>
            </div>
        </div>
