            Day After (Sunday the 28th of August): Cool-down
        </h2>
        <div class="details-group l-grid">
            <div class="l-grid-u">
                <p class="details-content">
                    After a good sleep, we can gather for a light brunch in Persiceto.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="l-grid-u">
                <address class="details-content">
                    <b><a href="http://www.birradiclasse.com/aula/">Aula - Birra di Classe</a></b><br>
                    <a href="https://www.google.fr/maps/place/Circonvallazione+Italia,+50,+40017+San+Giovanni+in+Persiceto+BO,+Italy/@44.6371753,11.1876317,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m2!3m1!1s0x477fc5aa824cf54b:0x2c8fb159ac53eaf8">
